          <div class="year">1996</div>. <div class="article-title">Light on butterfly mating</div>. <div class="source ">Nature</div><div class="volume">382</div><div class="fpage">119</div></p><!--citationLinks: case 1--><div class="citation-links"></div><div class="citation-links"><p class="citation-links-compatibility"><span class="google-scholar-ref-link"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Light%20on%20butterfly%20mating&amp;author=K%20Arikawa&amp;author=D%20Suyama&amp;author=T.%20Fujii&amp;publication_year=1996&amp;journal=Nature&amp;volume=382&amp;pages=119" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></span></p><div class="crossref-doi js-ref-link"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1038/382119a0" target="_blank">Crossref</a></div><div class="adsDoiReference hide"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/basic_connect?qsearch=10.1038%2F382119a0" target="_blank">Search ADS</a></div><div class="xslopenurl empty-target"><span class="inst-open-url-holders" data-targetId="10.1038%2F382119a0"> </span></div><p class="citation-links-compatibility"><span class="worldcat-reference-ref-link js-worldcat-preview-ref-link" style="display:none"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=ti:Light%20on%20butterfly%20mating&amp;qt=advanced&amp;dblist=638" target="_blank">WorldCat</a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div content-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6" class="js-splitview-ref-item" data-legacy-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6"><div class="refLink-parent"><span class="refLink"><a name="jumplink-I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6" href="javascript:;" aria-label="jumplink-I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6" data-id=""></a></span></div><div class="ref false"><div id="ref-auto-I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6" class="ref-content " data-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-ARIKAWA6"><span class="label title-label">6</span><div class="mixed-citation citation"><p class="mixed-c