          <div class="year">1997</div>. <div class="article-title">Hindsight by genitalia: Photo-guided copulation in butterflies</div>. <div class="source ">Journal of Comparative Physiology A</div><div class="volume">180</div><div class="fpage">295</div><div class="lpage">299</div>.</p><!--citationLinks: case 1--><div class="citation-links"></div><div class="citation-links"><p class="citation-links-compatibility"><span class="google-scholar-ref-link"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="https://scholar.google.com/scholar_lookup?title=Hindsight%20by%20genitalia%3A%20Photo-guided%20copulation%20in%20butterflies&amp;author=K.%20Arikawa&amp;publication_year=1997&amp;journal=Journal%20of%20Comparative%20Physiology%20A&amp;volume=180&amp;pages=295-299" target="_blank">Google Scholar</a></span></p><div class="crossref-doi js-ref-link"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://dx.doi.org/10.1007/s003590050049" target="_blank">Crossref</a></div><div class="adsDoiReference hide"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="http://adsabs.harvard.edu/cgi-bin/basic_connect?qsearch=10.1007%2Fs003590050049" target="_blank">Search ADS</a></div><div class="xslopenurl empty-target"><span class="inst-open-url-holders" data-targetId="10.1007%2Fs003590050049"> </span></div><p class="citation-links-compatibility"><span class="worldcat-reference-ref-link js-worldcat-preview-ref-link" style="display:none"><a class="openInAnotherWindow" href="https://www.worldcat.org/search?q=ti:Hindsight%20by%20genitalia%3A%20Photo-guided%20copulation%20in%20butterflies&amp;qt=advanced&amp;dblist=638" target="_blank">WorldCat</a></span></p></div></div></div></div></div><div content-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1" class="js-splitview-ref-item" data-legacy-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1"><div class="refLink-parent"><span class="refLink"><a name="jumplink-I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1" href="javascript:;" aria-label="jumplink-I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1" data-id=""></a></span></div><div class="ref false"><div id="ref-auto-I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1" class="ref-content " data-id="I0006-3568-51-3-219-EAKIN1"><span class="label title-label">7</span><div class="mixed-citation citation"><p class="mixed-citation-compatibility">
          <span class="person-group">
            <div class="name">
              <div class="surname">Eakin</div>
